name: Cell In Love
description:
Visualization of the cells in my body when I'm in love.
Showing a live screen of what I saw with my eyes: on a video call with my boyfriend.
Why did I choose a cat as my cell? because cats are moody animals, a representation of the many feelings I have.
Gratitude for having a boyfriend makes me happy and this is also the main inspiration for me to make this work of art.
